*xfce4-4.4.3 (10 Nov 2008)

  10 Nov 2008; Christoph Mende <angelos@gentoo.org> +xfce4-4.4.3.ebuild:
  Xfce-4.4.3 meta ebuild

  22 Jun 2008; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org> xfce4-4.4.2.ebuild:
  Killed xfce44.eclass usage for meta ebuild. Move xfce4-icon-theme
  and xfwm4-themes to x11-themes. Move terminal to x11-terms. Move
  xfprint to net-print. Move orage to app-office.

  20 Mar 2008; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org> xfce4-4.4.2.ebuild:
  Relax Thunar dep so 0.8.0 is also allowed.

  17 Dec 2007; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> xfce4-4.4.2.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #201747).

